  "id": "RAW_a31ef47b",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-12-10）：Mistral AI 开源 Devstral Small 2，以轻量架构赋能软件工程全流程自动化",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500808&idx=1&sn=d1946efcdb10907a0188467573e0a0d6",
  "date": "2025-12-10 09:43:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Devstral Small 2</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"486\" data-imgfileid=\"100017142\" data-ratio=\"0.4185185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=03e5cf1f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxOINAzuxgTyQFCpbgxpbtNC34CwYMZFa1tTicxd63emyxN3I1ffnvzaJxQzt8tRAZXyQicAGS8wdjw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Devstral Small 2 是一个专为软件工程任务设计的Agent型大语言模型。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">使用工具探索代码库</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">、</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">编辑多个文件</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">以及</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">支持软件工程Agent</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">方面表现出色。它经过微调以遵循指令，非常适合用于聊天、Agent和基于指令的任务。模型具有24亿参数，足够轻量，可以在单个RTX 4090或32GB RAM的Mac上运行，适合本地部署和设备使用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/devstral-small\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/devstral-small</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：GLM-ASR-Nano-2512</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"518\" data-imgfileid=\"100017144\" data-ratio=\"0.44537037037037036\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fe51149d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxOINAzuxgTyQFCpbgxpbtNJQN5eemOjDCictcgqb22TwDW57LKsaJK6c39Y3iagwpH8vYwIicw6keTA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★GLM-ASR-Nano-2512 是一个强大的开源语音识别模型，拥有15亿参数。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型专为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">处理现实世界的复杂性</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">而设计，在多个基准测试中表现优于OpenAI Whisper V3，同时保持</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">紧凑的体积</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。其关键能力包括对粤语等</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">方言</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的卓越支持、对低音量语音的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">鲁棒性</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">以及在中文基准测试中的出色表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/glm-asr-nano-2512\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/glm-asr-nano-2512</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Fairy2i-W2</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"582\" data-imgfileid=\"100017141\" data-ratio=\"0.49907407407407406\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8b28246d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxOINAzuxgTyQFCpbgxpbtN83pTYTDJjnFe4Z3KdDk8mIGZrvuNVMlO7Cr6kqIibt7yPLBabzS8g0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Fairy2i-W2 是一个通用框架，旨在将预训练的实值层转换为等效的广义线性复数形式，从而实现极低比特量化，同时重用现有的检查点。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过证明实数和广义线性映射之间的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">无损数学等价性</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，该项目将标准的 Transformer 转换为复数域，并采用相位感知量化方案。该方案使用高效的四分之一单位根代码表，并引入递归残差量化机制，以迭代地最小化量化误差。Fairy2i-W2 在有效的 2 比特精度下恢复了 LLaMA-2 7B 的性能，几乎可与全精度基线相媲美，显著优于最先进的实值二进制和三进制量化方法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fairy2i-w2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fairy2i-w2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：siiRL</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"234\" data-imgfileid=\"100017140\" data-ratio=\"0.20092592592592592\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f805cd9b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxOINAzuxgTyQFCpbgxpbtNjzwvsL1YTiajycJQoQgFZ8mYA9C1CfdNxo6XAPAuIHlsFN94xmHE25A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★siiRL是一个创新的、完全分布式的强化学习框架，旨在突破LLM后训练中的扩展瓶颈。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">由上海创新研究院的研究人员开发，siiRL解决了限制当前最先进系统的关键性能瓶颈。通过消除其他框架中常见的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">集中控制器</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，siiRL实现了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">近线性扩展性、</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">显著的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">吞吐量提升</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">以及前所未有的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">灵活性</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，适用于基于RL的LLM开发。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/siirl\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/siirl</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Open-AutoGLM</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"780\" data-imgfileid=\"100017146\" data-ratio=\"0.6685185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=444c0716&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxOINAzuxgTyQFCpbgxpbtNYhNk05ThGljNaeTXrxjUOmZA68ia7yicIX6QEMnjdVj5jSTdAEqhz8Fw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Open-AutoGLM 是一个基于 AutoGLM 构建的手机端智能助理框架，能够以多模态方式理解手机屏幕内容，并通过自动化操作帮助用户完成任务。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">系统通过&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">ADB（Android Debug Bridge）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">来控制设备，以</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">视觉语言模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">进行屏幕感知，再结合</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">智能规划能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">生成并执行操作流程。用户只需用自然语言描述需求，Phone Agent 即可自动解析意图、理解当前界面、规划下一步动作并完成整个流程。系统还内置敏感操作确认机制，并支持在登录或验证码场景下进行人工接管，同时提供远程 ADB 调试能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/open-autoglm\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/open-autoglm</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Mistral Vibe</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"366\" data-imgfileid=\"100017145\" data-ratio=\"0.3148148148148148\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2460fe14&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxOINAzuxgTyQFCpbgxpbtN6WebPgBbsyVmHZyuoRRn8OKmBRp8AA96cMeIwRVvibBEk8TFMbQcV4w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Mistral Vibe 是一个由 Mistral 模型驱动的开源命令行编码助手，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">该工具集成了文件操作、代码搜索、版本控制和命令执行等功能，旨在提升开发者的工作效率。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它提供了一个对话界面，允许用户通过自然语言与代码库进行交互、修改和探索。Mistral Vibe 主要支持 UNIX 环境，但也可在 Windows 上运行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mistral-vibe\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mistral-vibe</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总了近期 Mistral AI 开源的 Devstral Small 2 大模型、GLM-ASR-Nano-2512 语音模型、Fairy2i-W2 量化框架、siiRL 强化学习框架、Open-AutoGLM 手机智能助理框架和 Mistral Vibe 命令行编码助手，涵盖基座模型、框架平台和 Agent 开发三大领域。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总了近期 Mistral AI 开源的 Devstral Small 2 大模型、GLM-ASR-Nano-2512 语音模型、Fairy2i-W2 量化框架、siiRL 强化学习框架、Open-AutoGLM 手机智能助理框架和 Mistral Vibe 命令行编码助手，涵盖基座模型、框架平台和 Agent 开发三大领域。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了六个最新的 AI 开源项目，主要包括基座模型 Devstral Small 2，这是一个专为软件工程设计的轻量级 Agent 型大语言模型，可在本地设备运行。同时，还介绍了多个框架和工具，如 GLM-ASR-Nano-2512 语音识别模型，其在中文方言识别和低音量鲁棒性方面表现优异；Fairy2i-W2 通用框架，实现了极低比特量化且保持 LLaMA-2 7B 性能；以及 siiRL 分布式强化学习框架，旨在解决 LLM 后训练的扩展瓶颈。此外，还提及了 Open-AutoGLM 手机端智能助理框架和 Mistral Vibe 命令行编码助手，这些项目在各自领域都展现出前沿的技术和应用潜力。需要注意的是，文章侧重于项目概览，对各项目核心技术原理和创新点的深入分析较少，更适合作为技术趋势的快速了解。",
